text: Tickle-U was a preschool block from Cartoon Network. It was the network’s second attempt at making a preschool block for kids, the first being Small World. The block aired for 2 hours from 9 a.m to 11 a.m and started broadcasted from August 22, 2005 until it’s final broadcast on January 13, 2006. Category:American children's television series
title: Tickle-U
